# Normalize line endings. The repo is LF-only (Biome enforces lineEnding: lf) but
# development happens on Windows — force LF on checkout and commit for all text so
# CRLF never enters the tree and desyncs local (Windows) from CI (Linux).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets Git must never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.keystore binary
*.jks binary
*.jar binary
